   (code DEGAS by E. Betak and P. Oblozinsky) that                5334 1451
   represents a good approximation to the DSD model               5334 1451
 - Exciton model with Iwamoto-Harada cluster                      5334 1451
   emission and Kalbach systematic angular distr.                 5334 1451
   (code PCROSS by R.Capote et al)                                5334 1451
 - Complete gamma-ray cascade after emission of                   5334 1451
   each particle, including realistic treatment of                5334 1451
   discrete transitions                                           5334 1451
 - Access to OM segment of the RIPL-2 library [Ri03]              5334 1451
 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                5334 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               5334 1451
   and gamma strength functions  based on the RIPL-2              5334 1451
   library [Ri03]                                                 5334 1451
 - Automatic retrieval of experimental data from the              5334 1451
   EXFOR/CSISRS library                                           5334 1451
 - ENDF-6 formatting (code EMPEND by A. Trkov)                    5334 1451
